content: Apparently alien craft have been spotted near nuclear installations for decades and will not let them release as the harmful vibration also goes out into the universe and adversely affects other planets and beings. So if they are protecting us there, perhaps if more of us 'asked' them to help, they would. We must speak our request out loud apparently. We have free will but few know that. Our free will holds power, especially when verbalized rather than just 'thinking it' in a mediation or prayer. Someone who manifests a great deal told me we must ask them to help us. Something like: "Of my free will I call upon benevolent beings in the multiverse to please come to Earth to rid our beautiful planet of the dark forces and the harm they are doing to us. Please eradicate the chemtrail process along with all of those who command it be done. Thank you, thank you, thank you." Can't hurt to try! ;-)

children.content: Rhonda Sherry Link has been sent to your DMs! Blessings
Rhonda Sherry I wish they would share with us a better, safer way for energy

Linda Mayer That actually exists already here but the dark controllers are keeping it from us because they are making money off of all forms of energy supply that they charge us for. Tesla knew, he created it, as did others who mysteriously disappeared. The deep state is losing it's grip thankfully, so hopefully free energy will be available soon whether earth based or from benevolent ET sources.

Rhonda Sherry That's  more or less correct  🙂 They are protecting Earth / Gaïa from nuclear attacks and damage to nuclear installations, but it is mainly a question of protecting Earth herself, so they are able to intervene without us asking in some cases. However, there are enough of us regularly asking for général protection of Earth that this alone gives them permission to act when really neccessary. 
Just one thing I would like to mention ...you can speak to the angels, galactics, ascended masters  etc in a normal, everyday manner. They are actually more "modern" than we are (no linear time once out of the Earth matrix  😉 ) so as long as you're polite and friendly just chat to them as you would family and friends  🙂  If ever you feel downloads coming to you, you can always say / shout out something like, "Yay, thank you ! Bring on the good stuff !" or "Thank you, bring me more !" with a cheary voice. You'll probably notice the download energies get even stronger <3
Rhonda Sherry  Exactly  🙂 Watch the Thrive films (1 & 2) for great info on free energy and  look up Maxwell Chikumbutso from Zimbabwe  😉
Liz Euvrard For sure! I also learned that they all have quite the sense of humor too, so we can have fun with this and not feel like there are formalities. :-)
Liz Euvrard Thanks for the reminder. I've seen Thrive 1, will need to see the other.👍

Linda Mayer given that we have the power of the sun and the desert, I believe we do have access to clean energy. it just hasn’t been properly utilized yet. I think big companies with other interests stand in the way of progress, using solar
